---
title: Herby Lamb & Caramelised Onion Burger with Wedges & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: There’s something about a burger made with lamb mince that feels extra special. Juicy patties are stacked high with sweet caramelised onions and a creamy, herby slaw. Served with golden, crispy wedges, it’s a mouthwatering meal you’ll savour to the last bite!
